OL,6,CStage A
OL,8,GWhat is an orphan source? What was the
OL,9,Gorphan source incident in 2024? Why
OL,10,Gwere we so worried? Were there any
OL,11,Glegal ramifications? What has happened
OL,12,Gsince? Based on experience working in
OL,13,Gthe nuclear industry, this talk will
OL,14,Gtell the story of the orphan sources,
OL,15,Gwhere they came from, why we were so
OL,16,Gconcerned, what happened next, and why
OL,17,Gthe best intentions sometimes lead to
OL,18,Gradiological incidents. No blame has
OL,19,Gbeen attached to anyone involved in
OL,20,Gthe original incident, and aside from
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
